title: Netflix's Holidate Part Three With 90 Day Gays
description:
**This episode also avail as video on Crappens On Demand http://bit.ly/crappensvideo**
Matt and Jake from the 90 Day Gays Podcast are back for part three of our crossover Holidate three part recap. We hope you have as much fun listening as we had recording. You can catch the video versions over on Crappens on Demand. Find Matt and Jake at https://www.sissythattalk.com @90daygays @themattmarr @jakeitorfakeit

Our Patreon Extras: https://patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens
